            <p class="product__description">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Laudantium alias, eveniet expedita ea unde exercitationem tempore animi minus cumque ducimus, corporis voluptatibus vitae sapiente accusantium! Eaque ex veritatis dolor unde!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card__actions">
            <button class="btn">Add to Cart</button>
          </div>
        </article>
